result.notes:
Three surveys of Farnes East rMCZ site have been completed to date (Apr 2015): 
Cruise: Cefas_cend0412 Date: 9th – 13th March 2012 Data collected: MB 
Bathymetry Coverage (Contractor): None acquired to date MB Backscatter 
Coverage (Contractor): None acquired to date SS Coverage: None acquired to

2014-03-13 — 2014-03-31 Data collected: MB Bathymetry Coverage 
(Contractor): None acquired to date MB Backscatter Coverage (Contractor): None 
acquired to date SS Coverage: None acquired to date Video and Stills Samples
